<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1941-07-14T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1941-07-14T00:00:00-05:00" n="748" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d748">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">611.59A31/8</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The Icelandic Consul General at New York City</hi>
                                (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Thors</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">New York City</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1941-07-14">July 14,
                                1941</date>.<lb/>[Received July 15.]</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to inform you that I
                            have received a message from my Government that they consider it
                            necessary that a delegation be sent from the United States Government to
                            Iceland to discuss trade and commercial relations between Iceland and
                            the United States with the Icelandic Government.</p>
                        <p>I should appreciate learning at the earliest possible opportunity what
                            would be the opinion of the United States Government concerning this
                            matter.</p>
                        <p>Accept [etc.]</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Thor Thors</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>